summary: Being a committed software engineer for over 20 years, I decided to reinvent myself. I resigned and started teaching math. I graduated as a mathematics teacher (1st degree). Having four years of experience now, I never regret a day. Using my expericence as agile coach I help students to take control over their own development. Teaching really is fun!
